description_short:
The Resource centre currently runs:
-Therapy groups: Lego Therapy in Godalming and Social Skills groups in Hersham and Godalming for ages 5-15years;
-Leisure Opportunity Project for 18+ with complex needs;
-ASpire Social Skills Group (18+ with Asperger syndrome; the centre is based at Godalming but service users come from throughout Surrey; 
-ASSIST project (16+ Asperger Syndrome, based at Godalming extending in West Sussex; 
-Saturday Morning Club (to be confirmed). Please contact Resource Centre Manager for more information on each project.
